# Regression: calling a closure bound via `let` per-row inside a pipeline
# `map` (referencing a row column as the argument) fails with FUNCTION_001
# ("Unknown function: $tax") instead of applying the closure to each row.

query 'let $tax = ($p) { $p * 2 }; from [{ price: 10 }] map { price, taxed: $tax(price) }'
---
> +---------+---------+
> |  price  |  taxed  |
> +---------+---------+
> |   10    |   20    |
> +---------+---------+
>
